---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-8">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">About Us</h1>
      <div class="prose dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
        <p>Welcome to Manga Reader, your go-to destination for reading and enjoying manga online. Our platform is designed with readers in mind, offering a seamless and enjoyable reading experience.</p>

        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>Our mission is to make manga accessible to readers worldwide while supporting the industry and creators. We strive to provide a high-quality reading experience with features that enhance your enjoyment of the content.</p>

        <h2>Features</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Seamless reading experience with easy navigation</li>
          <li>Bookmark system to keep track of your favorite chapters</li>
          <li>Progress tracking across devices</li>
          <li>Dark mode support for comfortable reading</li>
          <li>Regular updates with new chapters</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Supporting the Industry</h2>
        <p>We believe in supporting the manga industry and its creators. We encourage our readers to purchase official releases when available and support the original creators whenever possible.</p>

        <h2>Community</h2>
        <p>Manga Reader is more than just a platform - it's a community of manga enthusiasts. We value your feedback and continuously work to improve our service based on user suggestions.</p>

        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>Have questions or suggestions? We'd love to hear from you! Visit our <a href="/contact" class="text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 dark:hover:text-blue-300">Contact page</a> to get in touch.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>